<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Mac on KALAQIAE</title><link>https://kalaqiae.com/categories/mac/</link><description>Recent content in Mac on KALAQIAE</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 15:36:46 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kalaqiae.com/categories/mac/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Mac Brew</title><link>https://kalaqiae.com/post/mac/mac-brew/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 15:36:46 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://kalaqiae.com/post/mac/mac-brew/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="概述">概述&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Homebrew 更适合用来装“系统级、全局通用、基本只需要最新版”的基础工具；但它不是万能软件下载器，也不是所有开发环境的最佳安装方式。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>最主要收益：可脚本化（Brewfile），换新 Mac 时更容易一键还原；同时减少手动处理依赖的成本。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>